OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FThe leaks and briefings in the run-up
OL,7,Fto the Budget were deliberate,
OL,8,Frelentless and grim. They also proved
OL,9,Fto be very misleading.
OL,11,FThe OBR did hand the Chancellor a
OL,12,Fworse outlook, but the hole it blew in
OL,13,Fthe government's finances was nowhere
OL,14,Fnear as large as suggested.
OL,16,F"In the event, there was no big fiscal
OL,17,Frepair job," says Helen Miller, head
OL,18,Fof the Institute for Fiscal Studies.
