OL,6,F"The decision to increase her headroom
OL,7,F(from #10 billion to #22 billion),
OL,8,Fwhen she didn't strictly need to,
OL,9,Fdeserves credit," Miller says.
OL,11,FInvestors have been concerned about
OL,12,Fthe sustainability of the public
OL,13,Ffinances for the past year. The market
OL,14,Freaction to the Budget has been calm -
OL,15,F"job done", in one sense.
