OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FBut while more headroom lowers the
OL,7,Frisk of the chancellor's plans being
OL,8,Fblown off course again, the OBR gives
OL,9,FReeves only a 59% probability of
OL,10,Fmeeting her promise to balance tax
OL,11,Frevenues with day-to-day public
OL,12,Fspending by 2029/30. That is still
OL,13,Fperilously close to a coin toss.
OL,15,FLabour MPs may feel cheerful this
OL,16,Fmorning - many businesses do not. The
OL,17,FInstitute of Directors says it landed
OL,18,Fbadly with 80% of the 500 members it
OL,19,Fpolled.
