OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FFor all the talk of reviving the UK's
OL,7,Feconomic fortunes, the OBR judged that
OL,8,Fnothing in this Budget will make a
OL,9,Fmeaningful difference to growth.
OL,11,FWe are now assumed to be living in a
OL,12,Fworld where the economy grows at 1.5%
OL,13,Fa year for the foreseeable future -
OL,14,Fwell below the 2.5% per year that Keir
OL,15,FStarmer told ITV News he was targeting
OL,16,Fbefore the election.
