OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FAnd the 1.5% growth world is not a
OL,7,Fhappy place. It is a world of "dismal"
OL,8,Fgrowth in living standards (so says
OL,9,Fthe IFS). It's a world of tight limits
OL,10,Fon borrowing that make further tax
OL,11,Frises likely unless a lid can be kept
OL,12,Fon spending.
OL,14,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies warns
OL,15,Fthat some spending pressures already
OL,16,Fthreaten to explode.
OL,18,FSpending on school pupils with special
OL,19,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,20,F(SEND) has surged over the last decade
OL,21,Fand is forecast to keep rising.
