OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FThe IFS says the government will need
OL,7,Fto find #6 billion a year by 2028/29,
OL,8,For decide to reduce or restrict
OL,9,Fsupport for children with autism, ADHD
OL,10,Fand speech and language difficulties.
OL,12,FMinisters will also need to decide
OL,13,Fwhat to do about the #14 billion of
OL,14,Fdebt local councils are expected to
OL,15,Faccumulate providing Send services
OL,16,Fover the next three years.
OL,18,FEconomists at the influential
OL,19,FInstitute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,20,Fhave said Reeves's Budget lacked
OL,21,Fambition.
