OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,FIn her Budget, the chancellor also
OL,7,Fpencilled in #4 billion of savings
OL,8,Ffrom running public services from 2028.
OL,10,FThe government says this can be found
OL,11,Fthrough "efficiency savings". Maybe it
OL,12,Fcan - but what if it can't? Police,
OL,13,Fprisons, courts and local authorities
OL,14,Fcould all face another round of belt-
OL,15,Ftightening. The past gives us reason
OL,16,Fto be sceptical.
