OL,3,CBudget 2025: The spending pressures
OL,4,Cthat threaten to explode
OL,6,F"The fiscal forecasts are predicated
OL,7,Fon spending plans that would involve
OL,8,Fnear-heroic restraint in an election
OL,9,Fyear, and a back-loaded set of tax
OL,10,Frises that almost entirely delay the
OL,11,Fpain," says Helen Miller.
OL,13,F"It's reminiscent of the fiscal
OL,14,Ffictions of recent years. I hope this
OL,15,Fis a government able to deliver on its
OL,16,Fplans. But I have my doubts."
OL,18,FThe government has a large majority,
OL,19,Fbut it has already shown how difficult
OL,20,Fit is to cut spending and it will
OL,21,Fdefinitely need to contain it.
